"Twiga Power Sarl intervient sur l’ensemble de la chaîne de valeur de "
"l’énergie électrique : production, transport, distribution, "
"commercialisation et services associés."
msgstr ""
"Twiga Power SARL operates across the entire electricity value chain: "
"generation, transmission, distribution, commercialization and related "
"services."

