#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:186
msgid "Pourquoi choisir Twiga Power ?"
msgstr "Why choose Twiga Power?"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:188
msgid ""
"Votre satisfaction guidant notre service fiable, efficace et personnalisé "
"quotidiennement."
msgstr ""
"Your satisfaction guides our reliable, efficient and personalised service "
"every day."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:197
msgid "Énergie garantie 24/7"
msgstr "Power guaranteed 24/7"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:198
msgid ""
"Une alimentation continue et fiable, même dans les conditions les plus "
"exigeantes."
msgstr ""
"A continuous and reliable power supply, even in the most demanding "
"conditions."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:204
msgid "Solutions personnalisées"
msgstr "Tailor-made solutions"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:205
msgid ""
"Des offres adaptées à vos besoins spécifiques, quelle que soit la taille de "
"votre entreprise."
msgstr ""
"Offers tailored to your specific needs, whatever the size of your business."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:211
msgid "Maintenance rapide et efficace"
msgstr "Fast and efficient maintenance"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:212
msgid ""
"Un service d’intervention réactif pour réduire au minimum les interruptions."
msgstr "A responsive intervention service to keep interruptions to a minimum."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:218
msgid "Équipe d’experts locaux"
msgstr "Team of local experts"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:219
msgid ""
"Des professionnels qualifiés qui comprennent les réalités et défis du marché "
"local."
msgstr ""
"Qualified professionals who understand the realities and challenges of the "
"local market."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:236
#: twiga_power/templates/app/projects.html:17
msgid ""
"Découvrez nos projets de construction hydroélectriques, un moteur "
"d’autonomie et de lumière pour le Congo."
msgstr ""
"Discover our hydroelectric construction projects, a driving force for self-"
"sufficiency and light for the Congo."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:241
#: twiga_power/templates/app/projects.html:22
msgid ""
"Chaque initiative ouvre la voie vers un Congo mieux éclairé. Avec des "
"solutions innovantes et des alliances solides, Twiga Power rapproche "
"l’énergie des communautés et prépare un avenir durable pour tous."
msgstr ""
"Each initiative paves the way for a brighter Congo. With innovative "
"solutions and strong partnerships, Twiga Power brings energy closer to "
"communities and prepares a sustainable future for all."

